TO COMPEL THE PRODUCTION OF DOCUMENTS
AND INFORMATION IMPROPERLY WITHHELD BY
DEFENDANTS SHIFT4 PAYMENTS, LLC AND

LAW IN SUPPORT

ARGUMENT
...
I. Card Connect is entitled to production of all documents related to the "Shift4 Payments"
labeled merchant accounts, and payments from First Data to Shift4.
...
        Shift4's refusal to produce certain documents, including, but not limited to the
contemplated ISO agreement, all documents referencing any direct payments made from First
Data to Shift4, and documents related to the "Shift4 Payments" labeled merchant accounts, is without merit.
